title: Ep. 521 - Gokuldham's Musical Night - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal, with the help of Tapu Sena plan and organize Gokuldham's Musical Night. They invite everyone to the event. Popatlal misunderstands Champaklal and tells everyone that Micheal is coming to the event.

title: Ep. 522 - Babita's South Indian Outfit - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer and Babita are ready to celebrate Pongal. Babita dressed up in her South Indian outfit. Iyer and Jethalal couldn't take their eyes off her. Everyone in Gokuldham celebrates Pongal.

title: Ep. 523 - Gokuldham's Kite Flying Event - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone in Gokuldham flies their kite and enjoy the day. Iyer manages to cut Jethalal's kite and makes fun of him. Furious Jethalal tries to get back at him.

title: Ep. 524 - Kite Event Gone Wrong - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Someone in Gokuldham cuts the kite of another man. So he crashes the event in search of the culprit. Everyone hides and tries to avoid the Man. But there is a twist.

title: Ep. 525 - Finding A Bride For Popatlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal is worried that he's single and not able to find a suitable bride. Taarak and Anjali console him and reassure him that he'll soon find a suitable bride.

title: Ep. 526 - Baga Returns To Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Baga returns to Jethalal's shop and tells him that he lost his job. Nattu Kaka suggests that Baga work at Jethalal's electronic shop. But Jethalal refuses and tells him that there is no requirement.

title: Ep. 527 - Baga's Onion Scheme - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Baga sells onion on the road and tries to sell them for a higher price. Meanwhile, Jethalal tries to sell a Television. But Baga enters and tries to give 1kg onions for free with every purchase. Will Jethalal entertain this scheme?

title: Ep. 528 - Jethalal Is Not Impressed With Baga - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Baga tries his best to impress Champaklal and Daya. He does all their work fast. Champaklal and Daya request Jethalal to hire him. But Jethalal is still not impressed with Baga.

title: Ep. 529 - Good News About Tapu - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu gets a medal at school and gives it to Daya. Daya misunderstands and thinks that Tapu won the medal. She informs Jethalal and he gets sweets for everyone. Later Tapu reveals that he didn't win the medal.

title: Ep. 530 - Returning The Medal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal finds the owner of the medal and plans to return it to its rightful owner. Jethalal, Bhide, and Taarak go to Rathor's house to hand it over to him. The plan turns out to be small trip.

title: Ep. 531 - Why Not Hindustan? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham organizes a small show for the colonel. The wish to return the medal. The colonel arrives at Gokuldham and everyone introduces each other. He gets furious when no one says that they are from Hindustan.

title: Ep. 532 - Hindustan Society - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham Society performs its various cultural dances for the colonel. At first, the colonel is not impressed but in the end, he is moved to tears. Gokuldham proved itself to the colonel.

title: Ep. 533 - Champaklal Shares His Memories - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal shares all Jethalal childhood memories and embarrasses Jethalal in front of Tapu. Champaklal's friends visit Champaklal and reveal his childhood memories. Tapu skips school to hang out with Champaklal and his friends.

title: Ep. 534 - Tapu Misses Champaklal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu is at home watching Tv while Champaklal is out camping with his friends. Tapu and Jethalal miss Champaklal. Tapu suggests they go visit Champaklal at the camp.

title: Ep. 535 - Taarak Is Stressed - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak is stressed because of work so Anjali makes him his favorite tea. Meanwhile, Baga comes up with another scheme for Jethalal's electronics shop. Taarak is trying to finish his article but everyone calls him and disturbs him.
